54
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:25,339
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi k sebi te slabim glasom da ga nitko ne bi čuo kaže mi

55
00:07:25,339 --> 00:07:26,399
[SPEAKER_00] Bože moj

56
00:07:26,399 --> 00:07:30,160
[SPEAKER_00] sada vidim koliko je vaša ljubav za mene bila velika

57
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:32,939
