60
00:07:40,620 --> 00:07:43,079
[SPEAKER_00] koje sada ja spoznam u svojem bunilu

61
00:07:43,079 --> 00:07:47,180
[SPEAKER_00] molim vas za oprost i ljubim vas oče moj i spasitelju moj

62
00:07:47,180 --> 00:07:50,300
