81
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:01,299
[SPEAKER_00] ali poruka je ostala netaknuta

82
00:09:01,299 --> 00:09:04,879
[SPEAKER_00] i druga poruka je mnogo mističnija

83
00:09:04,879 --> 00:09:07,779
[SPEAKER_00] više govori o osobnom odnosu s Bogom

84
00:09:07,779 --> 00:09:11,500
